=== Stamens
- **Anther**: Contains microspore mother cells (microsporocytes).
- **Microsporogenesis**: Microsporocytes undergo meiosis to produce 4 microspores (tetrad).
- **Pollen**: Microspores develop resistant wall (exine with sporopollenin, intine with cellulose).
- **Tapetum**: Nurse cells in anther.

