=== Megagametophyte (Embryo Sac)
- Develops from functional megaspore.
- Typically 7 cells, 8 nuclei (Polygonum type):
  - **Egg Apparatus**: 1 egg, 2 synergids.
  - **Central Cell**: 2 polar nuclei.
  - **Antipodals**: 3 cells.

